# ✅ Step 4: Role‑Guarded Hooks (MOST IMPORTANT)

This is where **access is enforced**.

***

## ✅ Admin Hook (Gatekeeper)

```js
// store/hooks/useAdminState.js
import { useSelector } from "react-redux";
import { selectRoles } from "../selectors/publicSelectors";
import {
  selectAdminAuditLogs,
  selectSystemConfig
} from "../selectors/adminSelectors";

export function useAdminState() {
  const roles = useSelector(selectRoles);

  if (!roles.includes("ADMIN")) {
    throw new Error("Access denied: ADMIN role required");
  }

  return {
    auditLogs: useSelector(selectAdminAuditLogs),
    systemConfig: useSelector(selectSystemConfig)
  };
}
```

✅ Unauthorized components **crash in dev**  
✅ Easy to detect misuse  
✅ Clear contract

***

