# ✅ Step 7: Manager Role (Scales Naturally)

```js
// store/hooks/useManagerState.js
export function useManagerState() {
  const roles = useSelector(state => state.auth.user.roles);

  if (!roles.includes("MANAGER")) {
    throw new Error("Access denied: MANAGER role required");
  }

  return {
    reports: useSelector(state => state.manager.reports)
  };
}
```

✅ Same pattern  
✅ Predictable  
✅ Scales to many roles

