# ✅ Step 8: Optional – Route‑Level Protection

Redux hooks protect **data**, routes protect **navigation**.

```jsx
function RequireRole({ role, children }) {
  const roles = useSelector(state => state.auth.user.roles);
  return roles.includes(role) ? children : <Navigate to="/403" />;
}
```

```jsx
